  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diabetes mellitus

          -  chronic non-healing foot ulcers (&gt;4weeks)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Charcot foot

          -  Non-diabetic ulcers

          -  Ulcers healing under conventional therapy

          -  Sepsis

          -  Hematologic disorders

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Acute inflammatory disorders

          -  Chemotherapy
      </textblock>
